Fedders Corp said an offering of1,500,000 shares of 1.75 dlr convertible exchangeable preferredstock is under way at 25 dlrs per share through underwritersled by Bear Stearns Cos Inc &lt;BSC>.    The preferred is convertible at any time into common stockat 9.50 dlrs a share and is exchangeable after two years atFedders' option for seven pct convertible subordinateddebentures due 2012. Reuter&#3;